  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This video will showcase the Quick Sale ticket, including:</p><ul><li><p>Locating an existing customer: quick search or customers section</p></li><li><p>Adding a new customer</p></li><li><p>Adding ticket items: lookup, type, scan</p></li><li><p>Discounts</p></li><li><p>Processing payments</p></li><li><p>Adding notes</p></li></ul><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://youtu.be/C-GGr6D6Wuk\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/C-GGr6D6Wuk</a><h2 id=\"CreatingaQuickSaleTicket(video)-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h2><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1930494512/Creating+a+Quick+Sale+Ticket\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1930494512\" data-linked-resource-version=\"14\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Creating a Quick Sale Ticket</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933312070/Managing+Customer+Profiles\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933312070\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Managing Customer Profiles</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933803655/Ticket+Notes\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933803655\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Ticket Notes</a>  </p></li></ul>",
